# Instructions

## Create a Data directory

Run the following command to create a data directory:

```bash
mkdir -p data
```

## Download the File

Use curl to download an extract of the first Harry Potter novel into the data directory.

```bash
curl -o data/harry_potter.pdf https://docenti.unimc.it/antonella.pascali/teaching/2018/19055/files/ultima-lezione/harry-potter-and-the-philosophers-stone
```

## Install dependencies

Make sure you have llama-index installed

```bash
pip install llama-index
```

## Run the Script

Execute the Python script:

```bash
python rag-examples.py
```

Feel free to test the program with different queries.